phrases: I shall erase you from this world!
I would like to know that too.
And why are not you in class?
Have not you seen the message?
I have urgently summoned every single Exorcist in this region here.
The situation is of such gravity that we need everyone available.
A demon called Gale has infiltrated the Academy.
The Academy is protected by Sir Pheles' powerful barriers, so stronger demons cannot enter.
Either my barriers have a weak point, or someone from the inside invited it here.
That is something I would like to know as well.
I have ordered the teachers to track down Gale.
I want you Esquires to inspect all the barriers.
You stay and continue your training.
He said all the barriers, but how many are there?
Everyone is on it, but Neko's nowhere to be seen...
When I woke up he was not at the dorm.
He is not answering his cell either.
And he did not come along to fix the Kurikara.
He is not going to drop out of the Exorcist cram school, right?
Satan killed his family and he made a vow to avenge them.
I was shot with a gun!
If you accept me, guns like that will mean nothing.
With me on your side, you would not have to be afraid of the son of Satan!
Let us kill the son of Satan!
That is not what I want!
Why is a guy like him in my class?
Is he trying to take away my friends too?
Filthy demon... I hate you... I hate you...
Acknowledge and accept the darkness in your heart.
If you wish, I will help you anytime.
I got to get back or they will worry about me.
When your soul is shrouded in hatred,
I will have my chance to take you!
How long do I have to keep doing this?
Until you can control your flames at will.
Are you supposed to be here doing nothing?
Of course I want to join the hunt for Gale.
But I have been ordered to watch over you.
You really do not get it.
Do not think you can fool aroun -
The real thing is the best training.
It is not what you think, Yukio!
I was not trying to run away...
Do not scare me like that...
I cannot take this, my legs are giving in.
It must be hot out there.
I should wash my face too.
The barriers west of the school building and at the front gate are okay.
You asshole, who are you calling dangerous?
Dammit, do not screw with me!
Where are you pointing your gun?
He is the one you should shoot!
If you lose control, you will be...
If you hurt anyone around me, I will kill you without mercy.
What the hell are you looking at?
Hey, get a hold of yourself!
Do not worry, he is just unconscious.
Why do not you get that?
This is probably a portal opened by a key!
If this door closes, we cannot return.
You stay here and keep it open.
Damn, it is so friggin cold.
I have not seen you since this morning.
Where were you and what were you doing?
Anyway, get some rest today and get back on your feet tomorrow.
What do you think of Okumura?
He is acting crazy all the time, and then he dares to tell us to trust him.
To earn people's trust, you need... you know, something.
Sure he has a fearsome power,
but he is nothing special on the inside.
You should not be afraid of him.
Or... are you thinking of quitting?
How many times did they tell you that at the temple?
Your mother died protecting you even when the blue flames were scorching her!
You should at least honor her memory!
We still have half of the barriers to check.
Bon, what happened to your back?
I will just have to buy a new shirt.
This happened because you did not listen to me.
He will just repeat the tragedy of the Blue Night.
You do not want to lose them, do you?
We will defeat the son of Satan!
I went to the store and bought some manga.
I also got some more exciting ones so Koneko will not get bored.
We do not have time for that!
Why do not you get that?
I was reborn to kill the son of Satan!
I will chop your head off!
You are turning into a demon yourself!
I am fighting to protect everyone!
Do not let them fool you!
He is just jealous of your new power!
I am not Satan's son because I like it!
If you are afraid of me, there is nothing I can do about that.
But why the hell are you giving in to a freak like that?
You should ask for help from Suguro and Shima and your other friends!
Killing him will not bring back my parents...
I am not letting you go!
I am going to help him!
So in the end Rin Okumura saved Miwa?
Suguro and Shima both got away with light injuries.
However the problem is with the barriers.
Someone or something has infiltrated the Academy using keys.
Only a limited number of humans are allowed to use my keys.
I investigated the other side of the gate,
and there was a burnt down laboratory in the middle of the forest.
And not just any laboratory either.
It was a laboratory for artificial life research, that the Vatican banned 300 years ago.
We must investigate it right away.
And today we brought the beauty squad along too!
Where are you taking all that stuff?
It is none of your business.
The priests raised me as a part of their family.
I came to the Academy with Bon to pay back at least some of their kindness.
But I am a good for nothing scaredy-cat.
So I have decided to quit.
I would only because trouble if I stayed.
Did not you say that it is none of my business?
Do not say that to me.
I see you as a friend, you know.
It feels like hell if a friend leaves like that.
If a demon catches me again, I might do the same!
And you would still call me your friend?
So I will trust you too.
That is what being friends means, does not it?
To earn people's trust, you need... you know, something.
It is just like Bon said.
Where have you been all this time?
We have been looking for you!
Hey, do not you butt in at the best part!
Leave him, you will catch idiocy.
Who would you just call an idiot?
Koneko just recovered, so why do not you carry his stuff?
You are friends, are not you?
Is not that what friends are supposed to do?
W-Well guess I have to, then...
Nope, I cannot do it for guys.
I can only tell the fortune of girls!
